    schema1:description "Angharad joined Nuclear Restoration Services (NRS) in 2006 as a trainee health physicist. She spent eight years in radiation protection, including four years leading the department. Angharad then joined the Trawsfynydd lead team as EHSS&Q manager before becoming waste operations manager."@en ;
